{"_path":"/maps/_ai/prompt/team-based-instructions","_dir":"prompt","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"Team based Instructions","description":"为软件团队策划和共享指令（Curated shared instructions for software teams）","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"brief"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Brief"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"对在软件交付过程中已经积极使用 AI 的团队来说，下一步要做的不只是依赖个人的临时提示（prompt），而是要为整个软件团队建立一套经过策划的共享指令体系。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n这种实践可以帮助你把 AI 有效应用到所有交付任务中——不仅仅是写代码——通过共享那些已经被验证过的、高质量的指令来实现。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"最直接的落地方式，就是在项目代码仓库中提交专门的指令文件，比如新建一个 $$AGENTS.md$$。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n目前大多数 AI 编码工具——包括 Cursor、Windsurf 和 Claude Code——都支持通过自定义斜杠命令（slash commands）或工作流（workflows）来共享这些指令。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"对于非编码类任务，你可以在组织层面建立统一的提示词（prompt）库，让团队随时调用。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n这种系统化的方式可以实现持续改进：一旦某条提示被优化，整个团队就都能立刻受益，并且始终都能访问到当前最优的 AI 使用指令。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"来源：技术雷达"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"guide"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Guide"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"_1-为什么需要团队级指令而不是只靠个人-prompt"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"1. 为什么需要“团队级指令”，而不是只靠个人 prompt？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"如果只依赖个人经验，每个人在用 AI 时都会："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"自己摸索一套提示语，“效果只在自己头上生效”"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"新同事要从零开始学习如何跟 AI 协作"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"同一个问题，不同人问法不同，效果差异大，难以复现"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"而“策划并共享指令”（curated shared instructions）的目标是："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"把“用 AI 做这类任务的最佳问法”固化下来"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"每个成员都能一键复用，不需要重新踩坑"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"项目级别的“使用 AI 方式”变得标准、可复用、可改进"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"可以理解为：给 AI 建一本“团队操作手册”，而不是靠每个人即兴发挥。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"_2-agentsmd-可以写什么"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2. $$AGENTS.md$$ 可以写什么？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"一个典型的 $$AGENTS.md$$ 文件，可以长这样（示例结构）："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ol","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"全局原则（For all agents）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"代码风格（缩进、命名规则、语言版本等）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"安全与合规要求（比如不得引入 GPL 代码、不得上传隐私数据）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"输出格式要求（是否必须带测试用例、是否必须解释关键设计决策）"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"按角色划分的 AI 代理（Agents）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Code Reviewer Agent"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"任务：代码审